# Phaser 3 Fusebox Project Template

A phaser 3 boilerplate with hot-reloading based of [this template](https://github.com/photonstorm/phaser3-project-template), but using fuse-box instead of webpack as a module bundler.

## Requirements

You will need need [Node.js](https://nodejs.org) to run this application.

## Getting started

Run `npm i && npm run dev` from the root of this project to start the development server at port 4444.


